{"categories":["re-engagement","confirmation","thank-you"],"collections":"","description":"Express your gratitude to guests for choosing your bed and breakfast, hotel, or motel with this warm and personalized email. Perfect for enhancing hospitality and building strong customer relationships, this template confirms their reservation and thanks them for their booking. Ideal for motels, hotels, and bed and breakfast establishments, the email helps to re-engage customers, making them feel valued and appreciated. The confirmation aspect of the email reassures guests of their reservation details, fostering trust and reliability. With a focus on thank-you messaging, this template leaves a lasting impression, encouraging repeat bookings and fostering customer loyalty.","short_description":"Enhance your hospitality with our personalized email template, perfect for thanking guests for their booking at your hotel, motel, or bed and breakfast. Confirm reservations, re-engage customers, and foster loyalty with this thoughtful thank-you message.","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/LuanaLiguori.png","description":"Hello, I'm Luana, a graphic and web designer with 8+ years of experience, specializing in email and landing page design. My approach is marked by precision, proactive problem-solving, and strong collaboration. I create visually impactful designs that align with marketing strategies, including social media graphics, blog covers, and presentations. I also offer custom design services tailored to clients' unique needs.","short_description":"","display_name":"Luana Liguori","id":"luana-liguori"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"><!--[if mso]><xml><o:OfficeDocumentSettings